In Vuepress we can use flowchart plugin to draw flowcharts. Here are some examples which found in this plugin&rsquo;s site.
@flowstart st=&gt;start: Start e=&gt;end: End st-&gt;e @flowend @flowstart st=&gt;start: Start e=&gt;end: End st-&gt;e @flowend
@flowstart process=&gt;operation: Operation e=&gt;end: End process-&gt;e @flowend @flowstart process=&gt;operation: Operation e=&gt;end: End
process-&gt;e @flowend
@flowstart process=&gt;inputoutput: Inputoutput e=&gt;end: End process-&gt;e @flowend @flowstart process=&gt;inputoutput: Inputoutput e=&gt;end: End
process-&gt;e @flowend
@flowstart process=&gt;subroutine: Subroutine e=&gt;end: End process-&gt;e @flowend @flowstart process=&gt;subroutine: Subroutine e=&gt;end: End
